    <Descriptive_Notes>
      <Descriptive_Note>
        <Note_Text>Units of weight equal to 1/16 of a pound avoirdupois (approximately 28 grams). Originally equaled 1/12 of a pound in troy and apothecaries' measure, equal to 480 grains (approx. 31.1 grams).</Note_Text>
        <Note_Language>English</Note_Language>
